source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/shawarma-spiced-grilling-cheese-64d253237a42584bbbe507c2
author: HelloFresh
servings: 2
---

Wash and dry produce. Halve, peel, and thinly slice @shallot{1}; mince a few slices until you have 2 TBSP (4 TBSP for 4 servings). Peel and mince or grate @garlic{1%clove}. Roughly chop @pistachios{1/2%oz}. Trim and halve @mini cucumber{1} lengthwise; thinly slice crosswise into half-moons. Halve @grape tomatoes{4%oz} lengthwise. Zest and quarter @lemon{1}.

Melt @butter{1%tbsp} in a #small pot{} over medium-high heat (use @butter{2%tbsp} and a #medium pot{} for 4 servings). Add minced shallot, half the garlic, half the pistachios (save the rest for serving), half the @Shawarma Spice Blend{1%tbsp} (you'll use the rest later), and a pinch of @salt{pinch}. Cook, stirring, ~{1%minute}.

Stir in @basmati rice{1/2%cup}, @veggie stock concentrate{1}, @water{3/4%cup} (1 1/2 cups for 4), and a big pinch of @salt{pinch}. Bring to a boil, then cover and reduce heat to low. Cook until rice is tender, ~{15-18%minutes}.

Keep covered off heat until ready to serve.

== Israeli Salad ==

In a #medium bowl{}, combine cucumber, tomatoes, and as much sliced shallot as you like. Toss with a drizzle of @olive oil{1%tsp}, a big squeeze of lemon juice, a pinch of lemon zest, @salt{}, and @pepper{}.

In a #small bowl{}, combine @sour cream{1.5%tbsp} with remaining garlic to taste. Season with @salt{}. Add water @?water{1%tsp} one tsp at a time until mixture reaches a drizzling consistency.

== Grilling Cheese ==

Cut @grilling cheese{6%oz} into four large slices (eight slices for 4 servings). Place on a #plate{}; season all over with remaining Shawarma Spice Blend, salt, and pepper. (It's OK if not all the spice sticks.) Shake off any excess spice blend.

== Cooking ==

Heat a drizzle of @cooking oil{1%tsp} in a #large pan{}, preferably nonstick, over medium-high heat. Add seasoned grilling cheese and cook until browned, ~{1-2%minutes} per side.

== To Serve ==

Fluff rice with a #fork{}; stir in @butter{1%tbsp}. Season with salt and pepper.

Divide rice between shallow #bowls{}. Top with salad and grilling cheese. Drizzle cheese with garlicky white sauce and @hot sauce{1%tsp} to taste. Sprinkle with remaining pistachios. Serve with remaining lemon wedges on the side.